      <h2>FAQ</h2>

      <h3>What deposit amount should I charge?</h3>
      <p>For flash or small pieces, $50-$100 flat fee. For custom work, 25-50% of the estimated total. The deposit must be high enough that clients think twice before skipping.</p>

      <h3>Should deposits be refundable?</h3>
      <p>Non-refundable but transferable. If the client reschedules with 48+ hours notice, the deposit moves to the new date. This is fair to both parties.</p>

      <h3>How do I handle repeat no-shows?</h3>
      <p>After two no-shows, require full prepayment for future bookings. Your CRM should auto-flag these clients so you don't have to track them manually.</p>

      <h3>Do automated reminders really work?</h3>
